Dummy module to show how to write your own extension or override some files.

classes - if you want to override kernel classes, create a file in the classes folder and define it's path in var/autoloads/lhextension_autoload.php file

design - here you can override the default templates

modules - contains an example of how to write your own module, or override the default module files.

callbacks - callbacks then something happens. At the moment there are only chat_close callback. It get's included then chat is closed. You can have your own logic there. E.g send request with XML to some service.

To activate a module-

Adjust the settings to the following:

'extensions' =>
      array (
        0 => 'customstatus',
),